<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Δημήτριος καὶ Παυσανίας Παυσαν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ί</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αι</unclear> 

    <lb n="2"/>τῶι πατρὶ πλεῖστα χαίρειν καὶ <expan>ὑγι<ex cert="high">αίνειν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="3"/><subst><add place="inline">ᾗ</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> ἡμέρᾳ ἐξέστης ἡμῶν πεπράκα-

    <lb n="4"/>μεν <expan>χό<ex cert="high">ας</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num> ξένοις προσώποις ἐν οἷς 

    <lb n="5"/>ἦν καὶ πολλὰ λέα οἰνάρια <del rend="erasure">ὥστε</del> <add place="supralinear">ἐκ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="5">ε</num> μετὰ</add> 

    <lb n="6"/><add place="supralinear">χάριτος, ὥστε</add> <subst><add place="inline">αἱ</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> πράσεις ἡμῶν καλλιότεραι γε-

    <lb n="7"/>γ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied>νασι <add place="supralinear"><choice><corr>λίαν</corr><sic>λειαν</sic></choice></add>, <subst><add place="inline">καὶ</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">ἐλπίζομεν</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>λπιζομεν</del></subst> ὅτι 

    <lb n="8"/>καλλιότεραι τούτων γενήσονται. 

    <lb n="9"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸ γ</supplied>ράφομέν σοι ἵν᾽ εἰδῇς πό-

    <lb n="10"/>τερόν σε δεῖ ἀνενέγκαι τὸ ὅλον 

    <lb n="11"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἢ</supplied> μέρος εἰς τὴν πόλιν. καλῶς 

    <lb n="12"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ὲ ποιήσεις ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">άσε</unclear>ις ἐν Πέλα 

    <lb n="13"/><del rend="erasure"> <gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del>, ἵνα <subst><add place="inline">πραθῇ</add><del rend="corrected">πρ<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>η</del></subst> <del rend="erasure"><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del> τὰ τῆς 

    <lb n="14"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ετάρτης ληνοῦ μόνης. ἐπιγνοὺς 

    <lb n="15"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οὖ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> τὸν παρὰ σοὶ ἀέρα ἱκανὸς ἔσῃ 

    <lb n="16"/>περὶ πάντων. <subst><add place="inline"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Μ</unclear>ου<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νάτιο</unclear>ς</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ου<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νατιο</unclear>ς</del></subst> δὲ 

    <lb n="17"/>ὁ φίλος συντυχὼν ἔλεγεν συμ-

    <lb n="18"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πε</supplied>φωνηκέναι τοῖς ἐκ τῆς κώ-

    <lb n="19"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear>ς αὐτοῦ μετὰ χάριτος τοῖς ο-

    <lb n="20"/><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>κ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="32">λβ</num>. <expan>ἔρρω<ex cert="high">σο</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="21"/><handShift new="m2"/> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost"><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> </supplied><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> Γ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αίου</unclear> <del rend="erasure"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Τιβερίου</unclear></del> Καίσαρος Αὐτοκράτορος Σεβα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>τοῦ

    <lb n="22"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Παῦ</supplied>νι <num value="2"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">β</unclear></num><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0040" notBefore="0037" type="textDate">37 - 40</date></p></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Tage: 14. - 23. Juni. Zur Datierung vgl. Kienast, Römische Kaisertabelle (1996), S. 85.</p></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1672</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">21965</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1672</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;14;1672" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">143</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations">Olsson, Papyrusbriefe (1925) 24</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.21965" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>